
   Stats are the single most important characteristic of a player.
   They are listed on the score and stats command, you can type
   "score" to see your basic stats or to see a more detailed
   list of your stats type "stats".

   There are eight total stats, they are strength, wisdom, dexterity,
   intellect, focus, agility, primal and stamina. To see an
   explanation of what stats do type "help stats info"

   Your stats will start fairly low, however with each level you are
   allowed to increase your stats however you choose by praying
   for them at the church. "help church"

   All of your skill and spell abililities are based on the stats that
   they require, for information type "help skills".

   See 'help levels','help stats info','help maxstats'
